{"tid":162854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓別怕限韓令！專家：看看台灣經驗","createTime":"2017-03-19T14:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T14:17:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1db7752a0894e9e501aacd49392f18cae20751fc","tid":162854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpcaKhzw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpcaKhzw.jpg&h=4b9b1757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中客不來，台灣整體觀光表現仍不俗。圖為旅遊熱門景點墾丁。（資料照，記者蔡宗憲攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n2017-03-19  10:58<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓部署薩德飛彈系統，引發中國不滿，祭出「限韓令」報復，企圖全面抵制赴韓旅遊、娛樂、文化等產業。傳出中國從3月15日起禁止旅行社推廣赴韓，業界預計中客赴韓人數將減少600萬人次。對此有經濟分析師認為，南韓可以效法台灣經驗，減緩衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/mar/19/images/bigPic/400_400/phpxhzkXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fmar%2F19%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpxhzkXm.jpg&h=7d7b75af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國祭出「限韓令」報復，企圖全面抵制赴韓旅遊、娛樂、文化等產業。（歐新社）</span><br />\n《鏡傳媒》報導，限韓令及中國禁止赴南韓低價團，導致大韓航空和韓亞航空都出現往返中國航班訂位數減少約1成。英國經濟顧問公司「凱投宏觀」估計，去年赴韓中客超過800萬人次，約佔外籍遊客總數一半，中客消費金額相當於南韓GDP的1.3％，預估限韓令對南韓觀光業的影響，可能讓南韓GDP成長折損0.3個百分點。南韓IBK經濟研究所則評估，限韓令可能造成整體GDP成長率減少0.59到1.07個百分點，經濟損失約150億美元。<br />\n報導提到，「凱投宏觀」的分析師表示，南韓可以取法台灣經驗，台灣在政黨輪替後，北京當局也下達限縮中客赴台的禁令，但去年台灣整體觀光表現仍不俗，就是因為台灣對東南亞等地旅客提供更友善的入境手續，讓亞洲各地遊客赴台人數大增，彌補中客不來的衝擊。在雙邊貿易方面，雖然會有影響，不過效應僅限於短期，不至於大失血。分析師認為南韓不妨取法台灣經驗，從政策面因應限韓令。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009163&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a88ff55c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009163&h=49bffe59\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009163</a>"},{"pid":"40181cba15723a3cb8a77b76f58db01b358dd81e","tid":162854,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"幾時限港令"},{"pid":"e438aa20dbbb9c92261ccef2acb72d941ef8fa7c","tid":162854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a425b8018e3d37ebad47feb19e4c2aee575c795","tid":162854,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"原來韓國一年先得800萬強國人訪韓<br />\n香港一個月都400萬+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c5d698f1b1462a5b617afdc9eab8cd3d12956a","tid":162854,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e457eb0b795daac087561ae312b25b5543fc99","tid":162854,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時限港令</blockquote><br />\n除非香港可以裝薩德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5321112338fa42c12a921bac5e6ac9810cb4c8b","tid":162854,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾時限港令</blockquote><br />\n除非香港可以裝薩德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港都有導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/msw/htm_tc/ch02/images/pic17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fmsw%2Fhtm_tc%2Fch02%2Fimages%2Fpic17.jpg&h=c7458e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似話 強國喺深圳望過香港，見到打鼓嶺堆填區有呢支嘢，曾經以為係導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif